Privacy Policy

Travel Split – Trip Expenses (the “App”) is provided by Deepak P (the “Service Provider”) as a free service.

The App does not collect any personal information. It may collect limited anonymized usage data (like device type, OS, time spent in the app) solely to improve performance. This data cannot identify individual users. The App does not track your exact location.

No personal information is required to use the App. The App is not intended for children under 13, and parents should supervise their children’s use.

The Service Provider may disclose anonymized information if required by law or to protect rights and safety. Users can stop all data collection by uninstalling the App.

This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally. Continued use of the App constitutes acceptance of any changes.

Effective Date: 2025-10-03
